channel.title: Weird? Got a Problem Please Read - 2 questions also :)
channel.description:
Well there is two things i need.
1.) I downloaded Whitescape Source and CheezeScape Source and made it a icon on my desktop and when i click on it it opens the internet, then closes it, then goes to the little box that says " Open, save, or cancle." What do i do to run the source(s)?
2.) How do i download "client.java." Could some 1 give me a direct link that goes to the page that downloads it please.
-liam
